What i&#039;d like to see is tiamat be able to be built into a new item that might be something like this.

MELEE ONLY ITEM FOR THOSE THAT CAN"T READ!

Chaotic Hydra: 3600 G (Melee Only) FOR THE ONES THAT MISSED IT, IT"S RIGHT HERE MELEE ONLY!!! XD

Build Path
